rows.label: qst002504_msg0007
rows.name:
Wha- Hey, shaddup! Actually, I take
that back. I wish those monsters HAD
eaten you now!

rows.label: qst002504_msg0008
rows.name:
Mylak bad liar.
Already say "thank God"
when seeing Humhum safe!

rows.label: qst002504_msg0009
rows.name:
Just like Humhum thought,
Mylak brains made of only muscle!

rows.label: qst002504_msg0011
rows.name:
Bah... Why don't you team up with
some other climber, then?!

rows.label: qst002504_msg0012
rows.name:
But Mylak have great braveness.
Climbing even highest wall without fear.

rows.label: qst002504_msg0013
rows.name:
Humhum need Mylak as partner.
Mylak please stay with Humhum?

rows.label: qst002504_msg0014
rows.name:
Hah... There isn't a wall in Alst I can't
climb. You can count on me, partner!

rows.label: qst002504_msg0015
rows.name:
Thank you friends for saving Humhum!
Very helpful actually.

rows.label: qst002504_msg0016
rows.name:
Please, take this as thanks.
We owe you one big time.
